Build base URL:
```python
def logic_app_base(sub_id, rg_name, workflow_name):
    return (
        f'https://management.azure.com/subscriptions/{sub_id}'
        f'/resourceGroups/{rg_name}'
        f'/providers/Microsoft.Logic/workflows/{workflow_name}'
    )
```

Get the failed action from a run (for error reporting):
```python
def get_failed_actions(session, base_url, run_id):
    url = f'{base_url}/runs/{run_id}/actions'
    params = {'api-version': '2019-05-01', '$filter': "status eq 'Failed'"}
    resp = session.get(url, params=params, timeout=(10, 30))
    resp.raise_for_status()
    return resp.json().get('value', [])
```
